---
title: Veggie, Ricotta, Mozza and Chicken Flatbreads with Spinach-Arugula Salad
description: Marinara sauce and luscious ricotta with a kick of heat are a match made in flatbread heaven! After exiting the oven with crisp crusts and melt-in-your-mouth ricotta, these flatbreads are topped off with a refreshing balsamic-dressed spinach and arugula salad. Talk about a treat for the tastebuds!
